- Do not use the pages router use the app router instead
- Utilize the App Router for improved performance and simpler data fetching
- Implement server-side rendering for better SEO and initial load times
- Use `next/image` for optimized image loading and lazy loading
- Leverage `next/font` for font optimization and better performance
